  "texts": [
    "Therefore, the nuance of the relationship for each phase-property pair arises from the relative frequency of positive versus negative extracted samples.",
    "The performance of the LLM was evaluated using a manually labeled set of 50 sentences and ROGUE-L score, which quantifies similarity between two strings based on the length of their longest common subsequence [30].",
    "We found that the ROUGE-L score of the LLM for phase recognition was 84.08%, while that for the property recognition was 75.86%.",
    "Those suggest that the model performs very well at the NER task.",
    "These results were obtained using the final prompt where a total of 23 example sentences were provided to the model."
  ],
